- Latest Visual Studio 2017 is not supported by the latest CUDA toolkit as of 2017-12-06!
- From https://www.visualstudio.com/downloads install ONE of:
  - "Visual Studio Community 2017" with "Desktop Development with C++"
  - "Build Tools for Visual Studio 2017" with "Visual C++ Build Tools" 
  ! Just installing Visual Studio will not install the C compiler cl.exe !
  ! 9.0.176 only supports cl.exe versions 16.00 through 19.11, the newest VS has 19.12 !
  - For detailed version info: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Visual_C%2B%2B
